    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/4b5de1a9ba1909ad02282246fce21f29.webp?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=53 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What's the best way to go around as a vampire in this day and age? </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Finding suitable humans used to be a pain, but online dating has made the process much easier than it used to!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/8d198428cde89bdb5c508a4d1aebf91f.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a <strong>dating sim</strong> with a focus on <strong>narrative and investigation</strong>. Where you are living the life of a vampire surviving through online dating. Swipe wisely, match with humans, and carefully navigate a dating app to secure dinner. Avoid fellow vampires, manage limited daily matches, and control your growing thirst.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/3c72676e5624fac39a7b8ad94227e541.poster.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/3c72676e5624fac39a7b8ad94227e541.webm?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/3c72676e5624fac39a7b8ad94227e541.mp4?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/7702e41448e58a0c14c5610afc98e61f.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=74 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long forgotten are the days when you could simply snatch a human away to satisfy your hunger, but don't worry, <strong>no one can resist that wonderfull charm of yours</strong>. You just need to make your dates feel secure enough in your company so that they'll lower their guard and get to their neck as soon as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/0e64a79671123639b2bd1eb553a7e1ba.poster.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/0e64a79671123639b2bd1eb553a7e1ba.webm?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/0e64a79671123639b2bd1eb553a7e1ba.mp4?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/77b8e547a4c5aa1e81eeeff36f344a49.poster.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/77b8e547a4c5aa1e81eeeff36f344a49.webm?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/77b8e547a4c5aa1e81eeeff36f344a49.mp4?t=1738604766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/63f6cc1171395c5b8e082e8033fe0873.avif?t=1738604766\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes! Humans are not only food but <strong>potential lovers or even friends</strong>. We know the life of an immortal is a solitary one, so why not spend your days in the warmth of a lover or two? In Love at First Bite, you get to decide where your story goes; just be careful of not ending your days dried up and dehydrated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206530/extras/1956f458f9e79680b0ee34434b99ce7a.avif?t=1738604766\" width=617 height=405 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
